# Information about Markdown

The following links are to online markdown editors/viewers

    http://backpager.amasan.co.uk
    http://showdown.im

    http://dillinger.io/
    http://markable.in/

This site can be used to compare Markdown implementations:

    http://johnmacfarlane.net/babelmark2

A simple editor for Markdown and ReStructuredText markup languages
http://retext.sourceforge.net/
https://aur.archlinux.org/packages/retext/
